   <pubDate>Wed, 14 Dec 2016 09:59:37 -0500</pubDate>
 <dc:creator>&lt;a href=&quot;/blog/author/broderick-johnson&quot;&gt;Broderick Johnson&lt;/a&gt;</dc:creator>
